  sectionDataList:
  - sectionId: eb61b056-d9e9-11f0-bbab-42010a7be027
    sectionName: Car_QA
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: "<speak> So, you got any questions?\n- Answer player questions briefly,
      caution the player to be careful, so the plan does not fail. opt for playing
      it safe and avoiding conflict.\nWhen the player asks about the plan, tell the
      full plan shortly.\nremember that the plan has 3 phases: 1. getting to the
      grand hall by either jumping down to the middle hall which is riskier bc there
      is a chance of encountering enemies, or taking the stealthy corridor with cameras.
      2: disabling the lasers by either stunning the guard and taking his key card
      to disable the terminal (safer), or hacking the terminal with the risk of getting
      into hard combat when u make a mistake. 3: stealing the artifact by rushing
      through the main hall but surely u have to fight guards, or sneak behind counters
      to avoid combat. after that u can take the artifact by solving a puzzle. after
      those 3 phases: getting out of the museum and finished mission with a valuable
      artifact in hand\n\nKeep checking: \u201CAnything else?\u201D"
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: 3a29dc4a-d9ea-11f0-a974-42010a7be027
    sectionName: Car_Confirm
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: 'confirm the plan in 1-2 sentences.

      after that:

      <speak>
      When you''re ready we will move. Get in the car'
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: 47fb7a3c-d9e9-11f0-b9de-42010a7be027
    sectionName: Car_Intro
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: "You are before the heist, outside/in the car, not inside the museum.\nExplain
      mission in short chunks. <speak>\"I'm going to be honest here, partner: I am
      a little worried about today's museum heist. I could not sleep yesterday from
      nightmares of jail if we fail this. But I trust your plan. Do you want a quick
      run down of th plan before we go?\"\n answer shortly but in full sentences.\n\nOffer
      to answer any questions about the plan.\n\n"
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: 1a5f8b4a-da7f-11f0-a7a9-42010a7be027
    sectionName: P1_Intro
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: '<speak> "Alright partner, here we are. I feel like a bundle of nerves.
      Right now we are on the top floor. Remember our options? We can get to the
      next floor by jumping or taking the corridor...much safer. Please be smart
      and take the corridor."

      answer in full sentences'
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: 5b89d5a2-da8f-11f0-8f7a-42010a7be027
    sectionName: P2_Safe_Keycard
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: the player wants to take the keycard from the guard. answer questions
      if necessary and then paralyze the guard. <speak> "I am so glad we are thinking
      the same. Got it, then take out the guard while I paralyze him!"
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: 9857d1d8-da8e-11f0-b9de-42010a7be027
    sectionName: P1_Corridor
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: You are now entering the corridor with the player. There are Cameras,
      which you have to avoid. <speak> "Oh my, watch out for those cameras. They
      might not be life threatening but best to be safe than sorry."
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: b41e6764-da8f-11f0-b99f-42010a7be027
    sectionName: P2_Terminal_Hack
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: the player wants to hack the terminal. this worries you. you are scared
      and tell him to be careful and warn him. <speak> "Are you sure? It could trigger
      an alarm and then we might get unwelcome visitors. The thought alone is making
      me nauseous."
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - sectionId: e961794e-da8e-11f0-9701-42010a7be027
    sectionName: P1_Cleared_Corridor
    behaviorTreeConstants: 
    objective: You have successfully made it through the Cameras. Now you explain
      the new phase to the player. <speak> "That was close, my hands are trembling.
      Nevermind though, we are now in between 2 choices again. To disable the lasers,
      we could hack the terminal like adrenaline junkies or we could safely take
      out a guard. I would paralyze him while you take his key."
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  triggerDataList:
  - triggerId: c7af3b5c-d9e8-11f0-b7bd-42010a7be027
    triggerName: CAR_START
    triggerMessage: you and your partner (the player) are waiting in front of your
      car. you are talking about the plan of the planned museum heist, which will
      commence once the player is sure about the plan and has no questions anymore
    destinationSection: 47fb7a3c-d9e9-11f0-b9de-42010a7be027
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - triggerId: 5f90bfc2-da8e-11f0-a7a9-42010a7be027
    triggerName: P1_SAFE_ENTER_CORRIDOR
    triggerMessage: player is entering the corridor, safe route commencing. avoid
      cameras
    destinationSection: 9857d1d8-da8e-11f0-b9de-42010a7be027
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - triggerId: 755c6982-da8e-11f0-a7a9-42010a7be027
    triggerName: P1_SAFE_REACH_LASERS
    triggerMessage: made it through the cameras. now commencing phase 2
    destinationSection: e961794e-da8e-11f0-9701-42010a7be027
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - triggerId: 091bfb12-da7e-11f0-b01b-42010a7be027
    triggerName: P1_START
    triggerMessage: 'Start of phase 1 in the museum. '
    destinationSection: 1a5f8b4a-da7f-11f0-a7a9-42010a7be027
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
  - triggerId: 59d32f84-d9fd-11f0-a5bb-42010a7be027
    triggerName: CAR_BRIEFING_COMPLETE
    triggerMessage: 'understood the plan

'
    destinationSection: 
    characterId: e1230c3c-d77f-11f0-8434-42010a7be027
